Description: learning-by-testing to excess
 A learning-by-testing program to learn quickly, mostly memorizing 
 tasks like vocabulary. Quizdrill supports multible choice, simple
 quiz as well as flash card testing. 
 Quizdrill was inspired by langdrill.
 .
